					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Being a -J is fine to me; it does not belong in the mainlist.</p> </blockquote> <p>There are few things that infuriate me more than this statement and all of its variants, because I have to re-iterate the same rebuttal like I'm playing whak-a-mole.</p> <p>I will never write a -J. Ever. Simple as that. I will not write off any of the silly shit I write with a &quot;no, not really&quot;.</p> 
