					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This one is only character, which I don't think is enough.<br /> I am arguing that you can put this character into anything. ANYTHING. There is nothing unique about this stick, and its history (which is nothing). In my opinion it falls into the category of trying to be funny for the sake of it.<br /> Being a -J is fine to me; it does not belong in the mainlist.<br /> Downvoted.</p> 
				 	]]>
